graph LR
    ModelRegistryOp[Model Registry Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ModelRegistryOp -->|database backend| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL 16<br/>RHEL9]
    ModelRegistryOp -->|database backend<br/>alternative| MySQL[MySQL 8.x]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|TLS certs<br/>OpenShift only| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA]
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|TLS certs<br/>non-OpenShift| CertManager[cert-manager]
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|service mesh<br/>integration| Istio[Istio Service Mesh 1.20+]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    ModelRegistryOp -->|platform<br/>integration| ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator]
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|ingress<br/>when Istio enabled| IstioGateway[Istio Ingress Gateway]

    %% Kubernetes Core Dependencies
    ModelRegistryOp -->|CR management<br/>RBAC| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    ModelRegistryOp -->|external ingress<br/>OpenShift| Router[OpenShift Router]

    %% Integration Points (Consumers)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management<br/>future| ModelRegistryOp
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto-deploy models<br/>future| ModelRegistryOp
    KServe[KServe] -.->|model metadata<br/>integration| ModelRegistryOp

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|metrics scraping| ModelRegistryOp

    %% Data Layer
    ModelRegistryOp -->|creates/manages| RegistryInstance[Model Registry Instances<br/>REST + gRPC APIs]
    RegistryInstance -->|stores metadata| PostgreSQL
    RegistryInstance -->|stores metadata| MySQL

    %% Configuration
    ODHOperator -->|provides config| ServiceMeshRefs[ConfigMap:<br/>service-mesh-refs]
    ServiceMeshRefs -.->|Istio config| ModelRegistryOp

    %% Styling
    style ModelRegistryOp fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff
    style RegistryInstance fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    style PostgreSQL fill:#777,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style MySQL fill:#777,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    style ServiceCA fill:#cc0000,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Router fill:#cc0000,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style K8sAPI fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style IstioGateway fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    style ODHOperator fill:#0088ce,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ServiceMeshRefs fill:#0088ce,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Prometheus fill:#0088ce,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    style Dashboard fill:#d3d3d3,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Pipelines fill:#d3d3d3,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
